asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Zeke
description:
Little is known about how Zeke was turned, but it seems it must’ve occurred sometime around the time of the wreck. Last thing he remembers from before, was when he was fighting alongside his brother, Buster. The two of them were lieutenants under Thumper, and they were an unstoppable duo. As part of their attire, they chose to wear matching red clown noses for a couple of reasons: one was so, if they got separated, they could easily find each other amongst the chaos. And the second was a bit of a shot at their opposition, a way of clowning them as the pair ripped through their ranks.
However, somewhere along the way Zeke and Buster lost each other. Buster searched far and wide for his brother, but when he finally found him, it was too late. He’d already been turned. But how? That part remains a mystery.

Zeke now has a hunger for brains, and mycelium! His zombie thirst has him craving brains, but he eats mycelium as a way of keeping from losing himself completely. There are still traces of his former self left, so it’s his and Busters hope that the more mycelium he eats, the more parts of his former self might return.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

name: Peter Rabbitto
description:
Kia Ora, I came from a faraway Island in NZ called MoturoaRabbit Island. My whanau and ancestors were hunted by humans until near extinction. A few of us left and swam and swam and swam, until we found an out of the way and human free swamp. 
I swam so hard across the strait, something happened to my eyes. They crossed over too.
Lucky with my Tiger fur, I can blend into my new home in case the human find us here I think I might be ready to hop out of the swamp soon to find my one true love or many, or lots and lots. I also need to find a new supply of mycelium and carrots, I am getting low.
